snippet.title: Transcripted – Launch Trailer | PS4
snippet.description: Transcripted will be available on PlayStation 4 starting 13th September. Transcripted is a mixture of two incredibly addictive and vastly popular casual gaming styles: the dual-stick shooter and the match three puzzle game. More info on http://www.transcripted-game.com
